  <brief_title>CarboMedics Top Hat vs St. Jude Medical Regent Valve Comparing Sizing and Hemodynamics</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Study to Compare Sizing, Implant Techniques, &amp; Hemodynamic Performance Between the CarboMedics Supra-annular Top Hat Valve and the St. Jude Medical Regent Valve in the Aortic Position.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
